ji\" />"},{"pid":"f1256a48eedd559097db9be9e57919cf0c397537","tid":28650,"uid":48566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T15:59:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好易整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n炸？唔會好煩咩</blockquote><br />\n其實上粉煎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拎個袋落3茶匙粉，放8隻雞翼<br />\n不停搖，咁就會平均上到薄薄地嘅粉<br />\n我用易潔鑊<br />\n多少少油燒熱佢，先落雞皮果邊，中火慢慢嚟<br />\n煎左陣搖下隻鑊睇下有冇痴，冇就反轉，繼續<br />\n不過應該未上曬色，細火再慢慢嚟，金黃就食得<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71f02a9f36a5a03cb6acd8bf57ea723473c9c5de","tid":28650,"uid":39785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T16:12:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好易整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&lt;/blockquote&gt;<br />\n<br />\n炸？唔會好煩咩&lt;/blockquote&gt;<br />\n其實上粉煎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拎個袋落3茶匙粉，放8隻雞翼<br />\n不停搖，咁就會平均上到薄薄地嘅粉<br />\n我用易潔鑊<br />\n多少少油燒熱佢，先落雞皮果邊，中火慢慢嚟<br />\n煎左陣搖下隻鑊睇下有冇痴，冇就反轉，繼續<br />\n不過應該未上曬色，細火再慢慢嚟，金黃就食得<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}